# CryptoVault Environment Configuration

## Client (.env.local)

```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
VITE_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x...
VITE_CHAIN_ID=137
VITE_RPC_URL=https://polygon-rpc.com
VITE_PUBLIC_KEY=your-wallet-public-key
```

## Server (.env.local)

```env
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=5000
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/cryptovault
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret-key
PRIVATE_KEY=your-wallet-private-key
NETWORK=polygon
POLYGON_RPC=https://polygon-rpc.com
ETHEREUM_RPC=https://eth-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/...
```

## Deployment (Netlify)

Set these environment variables in Netlify dashboard:

```
VITE_API_URL=https://cryptovault-api.netlify.app
VITE_CHAIN_ID=137
NODE_ENV=production
```

## Polygon Network Configuration

- **Chain ID:** 137
- **RPC:** https://polygon-rpc.com/
- **Block Explorer:** https://polygonscan.com/

## Ethereum Network Configuration

- **Chain ID:** 1
- **RPC:** https://eth-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/{key}
- **Block Explorer:** https://etherscan.io/
